				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">What Song in Groups (Level 51)?<a name="48559"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jun 27 04 10:53 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Hallo!
<br />

<br />
My Bard is now Level 51 and i want to know which are the best Songs in ADV?
<br />

<br />
I use the following Songs at the moment:
<br />

<br />
1 Verse of Victory (50) (Speed, agi, str)
<br />
2 Largo Absonant Binding (51) (Slow)
<br />
3 Sionachie Dreams (40) (Mezz)
<br />
4 Kelin Lugubrious Lambert (8) (Lull, for pulling)
<br />
5 Shild of Songs (49)
<br />

<br />
I sing 1, 2, 5.
<br />

<br />
What do u think? Is that okay?
<br />
What else Spells would u use / mem?
<br />

<br />
Thank u very much for helping!
<br />
Rahya</span></td>
