				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: What Song in Groups (Level 51)?<a name="48863"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jun 28 04 8:11 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I am level 53, my standard 4 song twist is:
<br />

<br />
Amp
<br />
Haste
